text: Cosmic latte is the average color of the universe, found by a team of astronomers from Johns Hopkins University. Due to flawed calculations, the average color of the universe was originally thought to be turquoise. == Shades of cosmic latte == * Dark cosmic - a shade of cosmic latte * Cosmic beige - a shade of cosmic latte * Cosmic gray - a dull shade of cosmic latte Category:Shades of white Category:Cosmology
title: Cosmic latte
